Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.04,0:11:38.05,md,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\c&H000000&\pos(328,601)\fscx108\fscy117}(Aikawa Ayumu)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,Đừng tự giới thiệu nữa! Xấu hổ quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,Quả là thế. Kinh tởm đến mức ác ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.30,md,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\blur0.5\3c&HEEECEB&\1c&HEEECEB&\fscx146\fscy184\pos(640,530)}(Aikawa Ayumu)
